         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259">
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Hd1e108">Rubrica 33</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De fide seu firma credulitate religionis dei et diuine trinitatis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#P"/>De fide seu firma creduli
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>tate religionis et diuine 
               <lb ed="#P"/>trinitatis capitulum xxxiii:
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e123">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Moises in deuteronomio. ca. vi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e129">non tenta
               bis dominum deum tuum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Iesus filius sirach in ecclastico. ca. ii.</ref>
               <lb ed="#P"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e139">Ve peccatori terram in gredienti duabus 
               <lb ed="#P"/>viis ve discolis cordiscolis corde 
               <lb ed="#P"/>qui non credunt deo et ideo non protegentur 
               <lb ed="#P"/>ab eo.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e150">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem xxxii</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e152"> Qui credit deo attendit mandatis 
               <lb ed="#P"/>et qui confidit in illo non minorabitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e160">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Phylon sapiente primo</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e164">Apparet dominus hic qui 
               <lb ed="#P"/>fidem habent in illum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e170">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem. ca. primo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e172">servite domino in bonitate.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e182">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Marcus in euangelo ca. viii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e186">omnia possibilia 
               <lb ed="#P"/>credenti.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e192">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem xvi. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e194">Qui crediderit et bapti
               <lb ed="#P"/>satus fuerit saluus erit. signa autem 
               <lb ed="#P"/>qui crediderint in me hec sequentur et nomine</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e213">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Lucas. xvi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e217">dissit iesus discipulis suis
               <lb ed="#P"/>si habuereritis tatam fidem que tum est granum
               <pb ed="#P" n="17-v"/>
               <lb ed="#P"/>sinapis et dixeritis huic arbori et Â¶</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e228">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Johnnes. ca. iii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e232">qui credit in filium dei non iu
               <lb ed="#P"/>datur / qui autem non credit iam iudicatus est.
               <lb ed="#P"/>Qui credit in filium habet vitam eternam qui autem 
               <lb ed="#P"/>incredulus est filio non videbit vitam
               <lb ed="#P"/>sed ira dei manet super eum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e244">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem. ca. v.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e246">ait iesus qui verbum meum 
               <lb ed="#P"/>audit / et credit ei qui misit me habet vitam 
               <lb ed="#P"/>eternam / et in iudicium non venit / sed
               <lb ed="#P"/>transiet de morte in vitam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e256">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e258">Ait iesus si credidissetis moisi 
               <lb ed="#P"/>crederetis forsan et mihi de me enim 
               <lb ed="#P"/>ille scripsit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e266">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem. vi. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e268">ait iesus hoc est voluntas 
               <lb ed="#P"/>patris mei ut qui videt filium et credit 
               <lb ed="#P"/>in eum habeat vitam eternam / et resus
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>citabo eum in nouissimo die.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e289">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem. x. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e291">ait Iesus si mihi non vultis
               <lb ed="#P"/>credere operibus credite.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e297">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem. xii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e299">ait iesus ego sum resurrectio et 
               <lb ed="#P"/>vita.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e312">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem. xii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e314">ego autem veni in mundum ut
               <lb ed="#P"/>omnis qui credit in me in tenebris non
               <lb ed="#P"/>maneat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e322">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem in apocalipsi. capitulo. ii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e324">Ego fidelis vsque 
               <lb ed="#P"/>ad mortem / et dabo tibi coronam vite</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e332">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Iacobus. primo. capitulo. ii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e336">fides si non habeat opera 
               <lb ed="#P"/>mortua est ipsa. Tu credis quod vnus est 
               <lb ed="#P"/>deus / et bene facis / et demones cre
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>dunt / et contremescunt. Sicut /
               <lb ed="#P"/>corpus sine spiritu mortuum est. Ita 
               <lb ed="#P"/>fides sine operibus mortua est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e348">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Paulus ad romanos. ca.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e352">Virtus dei
               <lb ed="#P"/>est in salutem homini credenti.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e358">
               <cb ed="#P" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. x. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e360">finis legis est cristus ad 
               <lb ed="#P"/>iustitiam homini credenti / corde creditur ad 
               <lb ed="#P"/>iustitiam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e370">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem xiiii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e372">omne quod non est ex fide
               <lb ed="#P"/>peccatum est. 
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem ad galathas ii.</ref> Non iustificatur 
               <lb ed="#P"/>ex operibus legis nisi per fidem iesu cristi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e383">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. ca. iii.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e385">Omnes filii estis per fidem 
               <lb ed="#P"/>in cristo</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e391">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Ibidem. v. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e393">in cristo iesu valet fides que 
               <lb ed="#P"/>per caritatem operatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e401">
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem ad epheseos. vi. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e403">induite vos 
               <lb ed="#P"/>armaturam dei usquam ibi assumite gladium 
               <lb ed="#P"/>spiritus quod est verbum dei / ut s. eo. ca. xxviiii.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e428"> 
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem. primo. ad timotheum. ca. primo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e430">finis praecepti est 
               <lb ed="#P"/>caritas de corde puro / et conscientia bona et  
               <lb ed="#P"/>non ficta fide.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-d1e438"> /
               <lb ed="#P"/><ref>Idem ad hebreos. xi</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9259-Qd1e440">fides est sperandarum 
               <lb ed="#P"/>substantia rerum non apparentium. Sine fide 
               <lb ed="#P"/>impossibile est placere deo / credere 
               <lb ed="#P"/>enim oportet a credentur adeum / quia inquiren
               <lb ed="#P" break="no"/>tibus se remuneratio fiet.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
